%% Data Flow Diagram: llama-stack-provider-ragas
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Inline as RagasEvaluatorInline<br/>(in-process)
    participant DSP as Kubeflow Pipelines API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Remote as RagasEvaluatorRemote<br/>(in-process)
    participant KFPPod as KFP Pod<br/>(ragas_evaluation_pipeline)
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Inference as Inference Backend<br/>(Ollama/vLLM)

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation

    Client->>LLS: POST /api/eval/run_eval<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LLS->>Inline: run_eval (in-process)
    Inline->>LLS: DatasetIO API (in-process)<br/>Retrieve dataset
    Inline->>LLS: Inference API - LLM (in-process)<br/>via LlamaStackInlineLLM
    LLS->>Inference: HTTP/11434<br/>LLM completions
    Inference-->>LLS: Completions response
    Inline->>LLS: Inference API - Embeddings (in-process)<br/>via LlamaStackInlineEmbeddings
    LLS->>Inference: HTTP/11434<br/>Embedding vectors
    Inference-->>LLS: Embeddings response
    Note over Inline: Ragas evaluate()<br/>answer_relevancy, context_precision,<br/>faithfulness, context_recall
    Inline-->>LLS: Evaluation scores
    Client->>LLS: GET /api/eval/job_result<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LLS-->>Client: JSON evaluation results

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Remote Evaluation (Kubeflow Pipelines)

    Client->>LLS: POST /api/eval/run_eval<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LLS->>Remote: run_eval (in-process)
    Remote->>DSP: GET /healthz<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    DSP-->>Remote: Health OK
    Remote->>DSP: POST create_run<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token<br/>Pipeline: ragas_evaluation_pipeline
    DSP-->>Remote: Run ID
    Remote-->>LLS: Job submitted (async)
    LLS-->>Client: Job ID

    Note over DSP,S3: Pipeline Execution (async)
    DSP->>KFPPod: Start pipeline run
    KFPPod->>LLS: GET datasets API<br/>HTTP/8321 (callback)
    LLS-->>KFPPod: Dataset rows
    KFPPod->>LLS: POST completions + embeddings<br/>HTTP/8321 (callback)<br/>via LlamaStackRemoteLLM/Embeddings
    LLS->>Inference: HTTP/11434
    Inference-->>LLS: Model responses
    LLS-->>KFPPod: Inference results
    Note over KFPPod: Ragas evaluate()
    KFPPod->>S3: PUT results.jsonl<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS IAM

    Client->>LLS: GET /api/eval/job_status<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LLS->>Remote: job_status
    Remote->>DSP: GET get_run<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    DSP-->>Remote: Run status
    Remote-->>LLS: Status response
    LLS-->>Client: Job status

    Client->>LLS: GET /api/eval/job_result<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LLS->>Remote: job_result
    Remote->>S3: GET results.jsonl<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS IAM
    S3-->>Remote: Evaluation results
    Remote-->>LLS: Parsed results
    LLS-->>Client: JSON evaluation results
